CHANGES
=======

0.3.1
-----

* chg: backend properties now cached properties

0.3.0
-----

* new: dev: Cleaning TODOs
* new: Ability to pass queryset method from MessageIterator to underlying queryset
* chg: dev: optimizing sql-query number and making all as lazy as fuck
* chg: dev: \`select\_related\` and \`prefetch\_related\` in \`Inbox.\_get\_messages\`
* new: Message exclude support
* new: Message pagination
* new: Message filtering
* chg: \`mark\_safe\` wrapping moved fom \`Message\` model to \`StoredMessage\` class !minor
* chg: \`mark\_safe\` wrapping moved fom \`Message\` model to \`StoredMessage\` class
* chg: Message and Inbox models in Database Backend now class-level constants MESSAGE\_MODEL and INBOX model for easier subclassing of Database Backend
* new: Database message storage now provides \`replies\_count\` to message
* new: Database message storage now provides \`replies\` to message as \`MessageIterator\` !minor
* new: Database message storage now provides \`replies\` to message as \`MessageIterator\`
* chg: Database storage \`\_stored\_to\_message\` method now converts \`reply\_to\` from \`models.Message\` instance to \`message\_storage.base.StoredMessage\` instance
* fix: dev: flake8 corrections
* new: Template tag {% update\_last\_checked %} for triggering update of last check date from template rendering
* chg: No message-returning methods of database backend now updates last check date. Now you should manually trigger update via \`update\_last\_checked\` method
* new: Added function \`update\_last\` for manual change of last check date
* fix: Counts in context processor now execute queries only when used in template
* fix: dev: Deleted \_\_len\_\_ from MessageIterator
* new: Added properties to get sent messages and sent messages count at API, Backend, and Storage level
* new: Added methods for changing message state at API, Backend, and Storage level

